# IMAGE QUALITY SETTING (Still Photography)

## Renaming Custom Settings Banks

Rename selected custom settings banks.

1. Select **IMAGE QUALITY SETTING** > !Camera Icon **EDIT/SAVE CUSTOM SETTING** in the shooting menu and press **MENU/OK**.

   > ðŸ’¡ **Note:**  
   > To save settings for movie recording, navigate to !Movie Icon **MOVIE SETTING** in the movie menus and select !Edit Icon **EDIT/SAVE CUSTOM SETTING**.

   !Edit/Save Custom Setting Menu

2. Highlight the desired custom settings bank and press **MENU/OK**.

3. Highlight **EDIT CUSTOM NAME** and press **MENU/OK**.

   !Edit Custom Name Menu

4. Enter a new name for the custom settings bank and select **SET**.  
   The selected bank will be renamed.

## AUTO UPDATE CUSTOM SETTING

Choose whether changes to saved custom settings apply automatically.

| Option  | Description                                                                 |
|---------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| ENABLE  | Changes to custom settings banks CUSTOM 1 through CUSTOM 7 apply automatically. |
| DISABLE | Changes do not apply automatically. Any changes to custom settings must be applied manually (!Page 135). |
